OOC: StarJumper (Maximal battlecruiser) - Off the coast of
      South Africa. 

Hate to break it to you WW, but you were wrong.  Now who's in charge 
of this battlecruiser?

BIC:  Mustex jump up to yell and Rhesus grabs him and wrestles him out 
of vocal range of the transmitter.

Mustex: LET GO OF ME YA' STUPID MONKEY!

Rhesus: Shhhh calm youself my son.

Mustex: I'M TOO DANG STELLAR CYCLES OLDER THAN YOU!

Rhesus deactivates him momentarily and walks over to the communicator.

Rhesus:  Thunderstorm if they begin to speak again take notes, because 
you will have to tell us what it is.  There was another massing of 
metal to the South.  Perhaps a base.  We are going to see and keep 
Mustex out of trouble.

They begin off.
